--- !u!114 &1066338865
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1066338863}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7a48f13c3c74b4f7eb9ce291abdf24d0, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::WorldTrigger
  triggerName: NarrativeTrigger
  triggerOnlyOnce: 1
  fieldEnemyUnit: {fileID: 0}
  sequence:
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: '<i>The door closes with a small mechanical click. '
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: <i>For the first time since entering the building, there is no surveillance.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: <i>There is only the restroom stall, the muted sound of ventilation,
      and the brief privacy granted between procedures.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: <i>But hold on, there is one more thing.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: <color=#8B0000>Blood.</color>
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: <i>4 days earlier than what the application predicted.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: <i>Although not alarming, it is enough to make the morning feel
      slightly less controlled than it did five minutes ago.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 9
    speakerName: Player Options
    textContent: 
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices:
    - choiceText: 1. Take a moment and breathe.
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: first
    - choiceText: 2. Check the time.
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: second
    - choiceText: 3. Look for supplies.
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: third
    - choiceText: 4. Continue. It is manageable.
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: fourth
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: first
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: <i>Not a long one though. You are now running on company time.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstory
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: <i>Still, even a short pause can become useful to adapt.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: second
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: <i>There is still time before the next stage.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstory
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: "<i>But you can\u2019t hide in here forever."
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: third
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: <i>There are supplies.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstory
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: "<i>You don\u2019t need to get creative this time."
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: fourth
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: <i>Manageable is not the same as irrelevant.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstory
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: "<i>But it is often the word people use when they simply \u201Chave
      to\u201D manage."
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: mainstory
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: <i>Menstrual cycle tracker is now active.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 10
    speakerName: 
    textContent: 
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements:
    - {fileID: 432294781}
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 1
    activeDuration: 2
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 10
    speakerName: 
    textContent: 
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements:
    - {fileID: 1482113918}
    - {fileID: 100159665}
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: <i>Still, orientation remains ahead.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements:
    - {fileID: 1482113918}
    - {fileID: 100159665}
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 1
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: <color=#0953BA>NARRATOR
    textContent: <i>The difference is that you will now move through the day with
      one more variable accounted for.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements:
    - {fileID: 1482113918}
    - {fileID: 100159665}
    targetUIState: 1
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
