    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: It is not too late for you.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: That is the only reason I am speaking to you this plainly.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 9
    speakerName: PlayerOptions
    textContent: 
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: 1. Too late for what?
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: first
    - choiceText: 2. What happens if I stay?
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: second
    - choiceText: 3. Why are you telling me?
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: third
    - choiceText: 4. I just started today.
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: fourth
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: first
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstorytwo
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: For becoming part of it.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: second
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: You become useful.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstorytwo
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Then usefulness starts replacing the rest of you.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: third
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Because they chose you quickly.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: That usually means they saw something in you that they could shape.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstorytwo
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Or something they believed would not fight back.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: fourth
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: That is when it works best.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstorytwo
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Before you know what to resist.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: mainstorytwo
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: DIYU Group does not hire the strongest people.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: It hires people who can be made reliable.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: People who want to do well, people who follow instructions.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: People who can be convinced that obedience is professionalism.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 9
    speakerName: Player Options
    textContent: 
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "1. I mean, isn\u2019t this just how jobs work?"
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: one
    - choiceText: 2. You are saying they chose me because I would obey.
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: two
    - choiceText: 3. I am not that easy to control.
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: three
    - choiceText: 4. Why has no one stopped this?
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: four
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: one
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Perhaps, it is.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: "But DIYU Group isn\u2019t a corporation that aims for financial
      profit."
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstorythree
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: You will see soon.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: two
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: I am saying they believe you might.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstorythree
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: That difference is why you still have a chance.
