  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstoryfour
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Sympathizing too much is why people stay.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: optiontwo
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: No.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstoryfour
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: It is not.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: optionthree
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Because I still remember what I was like before I learned to lower
      my voice.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstoryfour
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: And because you are not gone yet.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: optionfour
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Reach the top.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstoryfour
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Not metaphorically. Literally.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: mainstoryfour
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: You see, this building is arranged like a hierarchy because it is
      one.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Every floor protects the one above it.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Managers, directors, finance, executive offices. The people who
      own the consequences without ever being held responsible.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: If you want to leave with yourself intact, you cannot only survive
      the floors.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: You have to reach the people in power.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 9
    speakerName: Player Options
    textContent: 
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: 1. The CFO and CEO?
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: branchone
    - choiceText: 2. The shareholders?
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: branchtwo
    - choiceText: 3. You want me to fight the entire company?
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: branchthree
    - choiceText: 4. And if I refuse?
      statReward: 0
      rewardAmount: 0
      targetStepID: branchfour
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: branchone
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Eventually.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstoryfive
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Before them, there will be others. People trained to make the climb
      feel reasonable.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: branchtwo
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Yes.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstoryfive
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: The people furthest from the work and closest to the decision.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: branchthree
    jumpToAfterStep: 
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: Yes.
    menuName: 
    encounterData: {fileID: 0}
    npcAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    targetUIElements: []
    targetUIState: 0
    isTemporary: 0
    activeDuration: 0
    waitToFinish: 0
    choices: []
    battleStartSound: {fileID: 0}
    battleLoopMusic: {fileID: 0}
  - stepID: 
    jumpToAfterStep: mainstoryfive
    type: 0
    speakerName: CO-WORKER
    textContent: "If that\u2019s what it comes to."
